videos.description: Esa Ahmad gets the ball and drives and finishes with a one-handed dunk early on against Kansas.
videos.headline: WVU's Ahmad slams one in early on against Kansas

videos.description: Josh Jackson passes to Carlton Bragg Jr., who gets past the West Virginia defense for a dunk.
videos.headline: Bragg powers through WVU defense for dunk

videos.description: Off a West Virginia miss, Devonte' Graham grabs the rebound and takes it the other way to hit a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Graham drains a 3 for Kansas

videos.description: Sagaba Konate gets the ball and cuts through the Kansas defense for a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Konate slams it with authority for WVU

videos.description: West Virginia takes its time passing the ball around before finding Nathan Adrian in the right wing for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Great ball movement sets up a WVU 3

videos.description: Devonte' Graham sends  a pass from beyond the arc to Josh Jackson, who capitalizes with a slam dunk.
videos.headline: Graham lobs it up to Jackson for the dunk

videos.description: West Virginia coach Bob Huggins breaks down what his team needs to do in the second half against Kansas.
videos.headline: Huggins: We need to limit Kansas 3-pointers

videos.description: Esa Ahmad knifes through the Kansas defense and finishes with a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Ahmad drives in for one-handed jam

videos.description: Josh Jackson tries to slam it home for Kansas, but he's unable to finish the dunk and the ball goes flying the other way.
videos.headline: Jackson gets denied by the rim

videos.description: Josh Jackson drives by the West Virginia defense and finishes with a strong dunk.
videos.headline: Jackson flies in for one-handed slam

videos.description: Nathan Adrian passes to Esa Ahmad for the layup to extend West Virginia's lead.
videos.headline: Ahmad's layup extends WVU's lead

videos.description: Daxter Miles Jr. drives down the court and passes back to Sagaba Konate for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Konate throws down a big dunk for WVU in win

videos.description: West Virginia's Nathan Adrian on his team's big victory over Kansas
videos.headline: Adrian: We know how good we are

videos.description: Postgame breakdown of West Virginia's 85-69 win over Kansas
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown of West Virginia's 85-69 win over Kansas
